---
title: Mexican-Style Chorizo and Black Bean Stew with Lime Crema and Zesty Tortilla Chips
description: Perfect for bringing a little heat to your weeknight dinner, this stew is packed with smoky goodness. Scoop it all up with the zesty tortilla chips to make sure no stew gets left behind!
